<p class="title">Chapter 5: Today's Fortune (No.05)</p>
<p class="para">Carrier: How dare they look down on people like this!<br>How dare they toy with people's hearts!<br>This is ■■■■■■■■!<br><br>Carrier proclaims in a loud voice.<br><br>This statement troubles Dark Mama.<br><br>Mama: Well gosh, even if that's true,<br>I feel like you're in no position to talk.<br><br>Carrier: And what is that supposed to mean?<br>What's wrong with calling out the ■■■■ for what it is?<br>I will admit those fortunetelling powers seemed to be<br>the genuine article, but using them to do evil is beyond<br>outrageous! Then again, I suppose those who choose<br>to believe are in the wrong too, hmm?<br>There will always be fools who cling to their fortunes,<br>so perhaps a bunch of shady fortune tellers comes<br>with the territory!<br><br>Carrier goes on. Dark Mama is astonished. <br><br>Mama: He and I might not get along so well...<br><br>Babe: His horoscope for today was pretty crummy.<br><br>Mama: I quite enjoy fortunes myself, but perhaps<br>he's taking it all a little too seriously?</p>
