<p class="title">Chapter 6: Maid's Diary: Fateful Job (No.06)</p>
<p class="para">XX/XX<br>Sunny <br><br>The queen summoned me today. She says it's now my job<br>to serve the princess because we're both the same age.<br>It's such an honor!<br><br>The princess has super fluffy hair and big, round eyes.<br>She's very pretty. <br><br>The princess was hidden behind the queen, but she said,<br>"Let's read a book together." So I read her a book. <br>She swayed happily as I did so. It was very cute.<br><br>Thinking about being here every day to help her feels<br>like a dream. My heart leaps in my chest.</p>
